# Raw research working files. Untracked because origin is a PUBLIC GitHub Pages
# repo that serves whatever it holds — there is no firebase.json-style ignore on
# that side, so tracking these published them at /pickleheads-research/*.json.
# They're working notes, not site content: methodology, named contacts and phone
# numbers, verbatim reproduction of Pickleheads' dataset, and explicit
# soft/unverified caveats. Nothing builds from them — assets/courts-data.json is
# the source of truth (see RUNBOOK). Keep your local copy; it stays on disk.
